Interface IOpMessage

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Serializable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IChunkMessage<E>, IHaltOpMessage, IOpLifeCycleMessage, IStartOpMessage
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EmptyChunkMessage, HaltOpMessage, LocalChunkMessage, NIOChunkMessage, StartOpMessage, ThickChunkMessage

    public interface IOpMessage
extends Serializable
    Common metadata for operator evaluation messages. Messages are Serializable since they are sent on the wire in the clustered database.
